import photo1 from '../style/background-text.png' import phot2 from '../style/giorgia.png' import Slider from 'react-animated-slider'; import 'react-animated-slider/build/horizontal.css'; import '../style/Carousel.scss' export default function slider() { const content=[ {'title': 'Pet Adoption App - Pet Adoption proposal', 'photoURL': 'https://res.cloudinary.com/duwtajcro/image/upload/v1618059396/fkrp0b2gcmwmvmkf2b31.png', 'description': "A full stack web application that allows users to list their pets for adoption, and browse other users pets. Registered users have the ability to post pets and contact other users. Styled with SASS, and the BEM class naming convention. Implimented admin authentication, allowing admins to view signed in users, add pets to the page, edit pets, and manage MongoDB data in a visual interface.", 'gitHubURL': "https://github.com/GiorgiaBorgmann/advanced-gallery-exam", 'deployAppURL': "https://giorgiaborgmann.github.io/advanced-gallery-exam/" }, {'title': 'Flicker Gallery', 'photoURL': 'https://res.cloudinary.com/duwtajcro/image/upload/v1618059515/ikhugqb7zjq6qo8bxqvb.png', 'description': "Front-end web application that display a image gallery", 'gitHubURL': "https://github.com/GiorgiaBorgmann/advanced-gallery-exam", 'deployAppURL': "https://giorgiaborgmann.github.io/advanced-gallery-exam/" }, {'title': 'NASDAQ Stock search ', 'photoURL': 'https://res.cloudinary.com/duwtajcro/image/upload/v1618060571/pvwedljt5frzaa8hel4c.png', 'description': "A fully functional 'Robinhood' like clone, that allows users to search and view public shares listed in the NASDAQ index. Users can view the market growth of any stock, via beautiful a user interface.", 'gitHubURL': "https://github.com/GiorgiaBorgmann/advanced-gallery-exam", 'deployAppURL': "https://giorgiaborgmann.github.io/advanced-gallery-exam/" } ] return ( {content.map((article, index) =>
